00Z","msg":"今日聽跟Katrina 同 new order <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果比心酸怎跟我比<br />\n我愛慕的卻是我知己<br />\n<br />\n想開心不必做富翁　她當天聽了沒法懂<br />\n更怪我仍舊是打工　不愛與我吃這西北風"},{"pid":"3a0864fb2c162fe1570e5c87eb5b733f3d0d3f10","tid":396312,"uid":3242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遊戲就算輸了亦有限<br />\n<br />\n每日都loop Eason 除左近幾年新歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總有一首切切底底講中，觸動我心</blockquote><br />\n我都係...新歌真係比較小聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9edfe9cf0321079d2def56a958c16ccebf71dc4","tid":396312,"uid":138013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃金時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你我永遠不肯定愛不愛誰 約不約定誰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37db64c998b6d6c5af26243e62b87a90935d1d2","tid":396312,"uid":26792,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:20:13.000Z","msg":"一起會鬧情緒 分開了為何依偎生命裏<br />\n致各位對舊愛仍有感覺的巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436555e8313aa595b6c7451e322f1aef5d5daa70","tid":396312,"uid":42465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人聽過忘記歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7109547a9d01a22a0caec8af7dfe7b85d15228a7","tid":396312,"uid":14511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人聽過忘記歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻再之後是什麼~<br />\n<br />\n首歌好開心"},{"pid":"506a8e70cd8cd690cb9ea7bd59017cdf32d16fe9","tid":396312,"uid":3242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HQILfU-MgRw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHQILfU-MgRw&d=Z9oVvM%2FKQPLTnR4gBvc82viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2329aa0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HQILfU-MgRw</a><br />\n<br />\n今日聽呢首(三首)---病態三部曲<br />\n<br />\n黃偉文之陳奕迅失戀三部曲一：大開眼戒<br />\n一個長相不是很好的人，喜歡一個人，但是又怕自己的樣子和人讓對<br />\n方不喜歡，所有在矛盾當中徘徊。不知道對方怎麼看自己，不知道對<br />\n方是不是喜歡自己，不知道......事實總是殘酷的，最後只能<br />\n說一句若你喜歡怪人其實我很美的感慨。<br />\n<br />\n黃偉文之陳奕迅失戀三部曲二：防不勝防<br />\n喜歡一個人到一定程度（那人不喜歡你的前提下）就會有點&ldquo;變態&rdquo;<br />\n了，她的一切你都想擁有可是都得不到所有只有&ldquo;秘密行動&rdquo;去&ldquo;擁<br />\n有&ldquo;她的一些東西。讓自己感覺是和她在一起的，說難聽點這就是意<br />\n淫的意思。<br />\n<br />\n黃偉文之陳奕迅失戀三部曲三：十面埋伏<br />\n經過那麼多之後，終於明白其實早就錯過了她，無論自己在什麼努力<br />\n的尋找都是沒有用的。只有等代下一個的出現了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉載自:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cloudsoo.com/blog/%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E7%97%85%E6%85%8B%E4%B8%89%E9%83%A8%E6%9B%B2%E3%80%82%E7%88%B1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%B1%E5%88%B0%E7%97%85%E6%80%81%E7%9A%843%E7%A7%8D%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cloudsoo.com%2Fblog%2F%25E5%25AE%258C%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2585%258B%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%259B%25B2%25E3%2580%2582%25E7%2588%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%25AA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2588%25B1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2580%2581%25E7%259A%25843%25E7%25A7%258D%25E5%25A2%2583%25E7%2595%258C%25EF%25BC%258C%2F&d=Z9oVvM%2FKQPLTnR4gBvc82viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f6e3d859\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cloudsoo.com/blog/%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E7%97%85%E6%85%8B%E4%B8%89%E9%83%A8%E6%9B%B2%E3%80%82%E7%88%B1%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%B1%E5%88%B0%E7%97%85%E6%80%81%E7%9A%843%E7%A7%8D%E5%A2%83%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%8C/</a>"},{"pid":"b826f8d3dd24d342df0af5bf280132c9cb5898f4","tid":396312,"uid":3242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gi