4T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑夜不再來 03年concert ver.<br />\n冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2Ar3G46prZo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2Ar3G46prZo&d=Z9oVvM%2FKQPLTnR4gBvc82viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2af7ebf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2Ar3G46prZo</a><br />\n補返條link先"},{"pid":"069c10387cf375da66a0d3222c46ad2c4bac6e76","tid":396312,"uid":3242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T23:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如不見 vs 好久不見</blockquote><br />\n兩隻都好正...難分高下。<br />\n岩岩失戀個期，試過係條街聽到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff725ba985a4988ca5ae9223ce922f941fa8a2c","tid":396312,"uid":103939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:34:09.000Z","msg":"成日loop duo dvd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c39e233c857f86d49a8f8dc397ed89c285d10f0","tid":396312,"uid":47145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如不見 vs 好久不見</blockquote><br />\n兩隻都好正...難分高下。<br />\n岩岩失戀個期，試過係條街聽到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩隻意境唔同，但係兩個故事都好正"},{"pid":"db620e6d51f3b69849e19dc8425b959fd0bdff48","tid":396312,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"呢排喺itunes買返以前演唱會既歌<br />\n<br />\n01 Easy ride<br />\n失戀太少<br />\n綿綿<br />\n黑暗中漫舞<br />\n活著多好<br />\n低等動物<br />\n<br />\n03 Third Encounter<br />\n人來人往<br />\n幾許風雨<br />\n<br />\n06 Get a life<br />\n最佳損友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw, itunes入面既Third Encounter live竟然冇最神既&quot;黑夜不再來&quot;<br />\n唔知點解<br />\n上網睇明明Disc 2第二首就係<br />\n<br />\n過兩日去睇下邊度有得買返呢隻LIVE既碟"},{"pid":"78dac65727452a71ac36657e67dc119828208f26","tid":396312,"uid":58520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日loop duo dvd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe too 雖然爛晒聲 但佢每首歌都唱得極度投入"},{"pid":"673d8e047dd1d550e7dcc368e9cf781c110e0fa5","tid":396312,"uid":67461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"baaf1afc686d8f0c74478efc3b710aea1ec5e702","tid":396312,"uid":3242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gAotCGoKhD0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgAotCGoKhD0&d=Z9oVvM%2FKQPLTnR4gBvc82viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4c82574c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gAotCGoKhD0</a><br />\n<br />\n今日聽---人來人往<br />\n<br />\n朋友已走　剛升職的你　舉杯到凌晨還未夠　用盡心機拉我手<br />\n纏在我頸背後　說你男友有事忙是藉口　說到終於飲醉酒<br />\n<br />\n情侶會走　剛失戀的你　哭乾眼淚前來自首　寂寞因此牽我手<br />\n除下了他手信後　我已得到你沒有　但你我至少往後　成為了蜜友<br />\n<br />\n閉起雙眼你最掛念誰　眼睛張開身邊竟是誰<br />\n感激車站裡尚有月台　能讓我們滿足到落淚<br />\n擁不擁有也會記住誰　快不快樂留在身體裡<br />\n愛若能夠永不失去　何以你今天竟想找尋伴侶<br />\n<br />\n誰也會走　剛相戀的你　先知我們原來未夠　藉故鬆開我的手<br />\n藏在貼紙相背後　我這苦心開過沒有　但試過散心旅遊　如何答沒有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">閉起雙眼我最掛念誰　眼睛張開身邊竟是誰</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感激車站裡尚有月台　曾讓我們滿足到落淚<br />\n擁不擁有也會記住誰　快不快樂有天總過去<br />\n愛若為了永不失去　誰勉強娛樂過誰<br />\n<br />\n愛若難以放進手裡　何不將這雙手放進心裡<br />\n<br />\n時間會走　剛失戀的我　開始與旁人攜著手　但甚麼可以擁有<br />\n纏在那頸背後　<span style=\"color: red;\">最美麗長髮未留在我手<br />\n<br />\n我也開心飲過酒</span>"},{"pid":"e36fc8335c46000938f3dc4e66aae9a9223aa993","tid":396312,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:23:32.000Z","msg":"任我行"},{"pid":"f17be191722562311f08eeeb40f57cbe29516948","tid":396312,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:30:21.000Z","msg":"幸福摩天輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知點解係外國聽到呢首歌次次都好想喊"},{"pid":"df3a348835ae272ee88